data.description: This home is on a corner lot in the highly desirable Creekside Subdivision in Lake Jackson. It has 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, new pool, storage building, 3-car garage, extra parking for boat or RV and so much more! The interior boasts granite counters, beautiful custom cabinets, huge walk in closets and wood-like tile throughout. You don't want to miss out! Call today!
